headline: Berkshire's Bite of Domino's Pizza Stock Isn't Cheap. 3 Things Investors Should Know
summary: Warren Buffett's investment success is hard to ignore, given the massive price increase of his primary investment vehicle, Berkshire Hathaway (NYSE: BRK.A)(NYSE: BRK.B).  This is why every new Buffett stock acquisition gets huge attention on Wall Street.  One of the most recent additions was Domino's Pizza (NYSE: DPZ).
